Paper: hep-th/0201222

Date: 2002-01-28

Title: On the unitarity problem in space/time noncommutative theories

Authors: D. Bahns, S. Doplicher, K. Fredenhagen, G. Piacitelli

Comments: 7 pages; typos corrected, sign convention changed on p.2

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B533 (2002) 178-181

It is shown that the violation of unitarity observed in space/timenoncommutative field theories is due to an improper definition of quantum fieldtheory on noncommutative spacetime.